# SET — Execution Governance

## Execution is the Missing Layer in AI Systems

Between intention and action, there exists a control boundary.

Right now, it is unmanaged.

---

## The Industry Assumption

If a system is correct → execution is correct.

This is false.

---

## The Reality

Systems fail not because they break —

but because they continue executing correctly  
on a state that is no longer valid.

---

## The Gap

Between:

decision → execution

there is a non-observable control window.

SET defines and governs this window.

---

## The Shift

SET introduces Execution Authority:

> A layer that decides whether an action is allowed to become real.

---

